divs: sighting detailson june 27, 2009, i was photographing with my digital camera, a sunset in a series of approximately seven photos. i saw nothing with the naked eye until i put the photos on the computer and one photo in the middle showed a strange saucer-like thing in the upper left corner. we were traveling west on co. rt 470 and the object appeared directly to the west and the photo said it was snapped at 6:50 pm on 7\27\09.
Summary: Photographing sunsets in a series of pictures; saw nothing until put the pictures on computer.
